<p class="ayah 76-4" id="4" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, We</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعْتَدْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[We] have prepared</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلْكَـٰفِرِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for the disbelievers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَلَـٰسِلَاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">chains</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَغْلَـٰلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and shackles</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَسَعِيرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and a Blazing Fire.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>4<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
