<p class="ayah 76-6" id="6" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَيْنًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">A spring -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَشْرَبُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will drink</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِبَادُ ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) slaves of Allah;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُفَجِّرُونَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">causing it to gush forth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَفْجِيرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">abundantly.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>6<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 76-7" id="7" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُوفُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">They fulfill</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلنَّذْرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">vows</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَخَافُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and fear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a Day -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ شَرُّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">its evil is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُسْتَطِيرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">widespread.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>7<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
