<p class="ayah 76-31" id="31" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُدْخِلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He admits</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَشَآءُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He wills</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَحْمَتِهِۦ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">His mercy,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but (for) the wrongdoers,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعَدَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He has prepared</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَذَابًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلِيمَۢا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">painful.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>31<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
